parameters:
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(This is definitely strange... How could something like that
actually be broadcasted... Was it because it was live that
there was no check? Or did they let it air as it was for
promotional purposes?)

\nc<Employee 2>And she's not even a succubus by nature... Because of her,
I've been too embarrassed to walk around with my head held
high lately.
\nc<Saki>(Ugh... I knew it would come to this...)

\bustMoveTo[2, -100, 720, 30]\nc<Senpai>Good morning, everyone. Saki, head to the reception room
right now.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Eh, what? I don't need to attend the meeting?

\nc<Senpai>Yes. The guests who saw the program the other day are lined
up waiting. Hurry on over.

\bustMsgExp[2, 3]\nc<Senpai>You all stop chatting about nonsense and go do some customer
soliciting. Or would you like to take some of Saki's
clients?

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>Eh, ah, haha... No, no. I couldn't possibly entertain them
all by myself.
